minutes of fame, but both are well met in the same way. Only White can be worse 
here.} f5 17. Bxd5+ cxd5 18. Re6 {This was considered clever once upon a time, 
but Leela and Stockfish don't blink.} Bxe6 $1 19. Qxe6+ Kg7 20. Qxd6 f4 $1 
{[%cal Bf4f3,Ba8e8,Be8e1][%csl Re1,Rg2] It turns out the black initiative is 
just too strong here.} *

