is also good for us too. Like a walk around the lake. Reading a good book.} 12. 
exf5 Nh6 $1 13. g4 $6 Nxf5 $1 14. gxf5 Bxf5 $19 {[%cal Bf5h3,Bd8d7,Bd6d5][%csl 
Rg1] With too strong an attack.} *

